<Layout
  title="About us - Boomger."
  content="About us - Boomger. - One Night Stand Entertainment, the innovative force behind One Night, the premier dating app designed to connect people for whatever they seek—be it a spark, a relationship, a date, a hookup, or a one-night stand. We are committed to creating an inclusive and dynamic platform that caters to diverse romantic and social needs."
>
  <main class="mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 max-w-7xl pt-8 pb-20 lg:text-[1.375rem]">
    <section>
      <h1>Boomger Community Guidelines</h1>

      <p>
        Welcome to Boomger. Our goal is to create a safe, inclusive, and
        respectful space where meaningful connections and healthy communities
        can thrive. These Community Guidelines are designed to protect all users
        and promote positive interactions across profiles, messaging, and
        location-based communities.
      </p>

      <p>
        By using Boomger, you agree to follow these guidelines. Violations may
        result in warnings, temporary suspension, or permanent account
        termination.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Respect and Kindness</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Be Respectful:</strong> Treat all users with dignity and
        respect. Discrimination, hate, threats, abusive language, or demeaning
        behavior will not be tolerated.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>No Harassment:</strong> Harassment, bullying, stalking,
        intimidation, or repeated unwanted contact is strictly prohibited.
        Respect personal boundaries at all times.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Authenticity and Honesty</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Be Yourself:</strong> Use your real identity and authentic
        photos. Impersonation, fake accounts, or misleading profiles are not
        allowed.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Honest Representation:</strong> Provide accurate information
        about yourself, including age, gender, and personal details.
        Misrepresentation undermines trust within the community.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Safety and Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Protect Personal Information:</strong> Do not publicly share
        sensitive personal information such as home address, phone number,
        financial details, or private documents — yours or anyone else’s.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Report Suspicious Activity:</strong> Report scams, fraud,
        catfishing, or suspicious behavior using Boomger’s in-app reporting
        tools or by contacting our support team.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Appropriate Content</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>No Explicit or Inappropriate Content:</strong> Do not post,
        share, or request explicit, pornographic, or sexually graphic content.
        Boomger is intended for respectful dating and social interaction.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>No Hate or Violence:</strong> Content that promotes or
        encourages hatred, violence, or discrimination based on race, ethnicity,
        nationality, religion, gender, sexual orientation, or disability is
        strictly prohibited.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Respect Intellectual Property:</strong> Only share content you
        own or have permission to use. Copyright infringement is not allowed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Interactions and Communication</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Consent Comes First:</strong> All interactions must be
        consensual. If someone declines to engage or asks you to stop, respect
        their decision immediately.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>No Spam or Manipulation:</strong> Spamming, mass messaging,
        scams, solicitation, or attempts to manipulate users for personal gain
        are prohibited.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Legal Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Follow the Law:</strong> You must comply with all applicable
        local and international laws when using Boomger. Illegal activity of any
        kind is not permitted.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Age Requirement:</strong> Boomger is strictly for users aged 18
        and above. Misrepresenting your age will result in account removal.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Reporting and Enforcement</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Report Violations:</strong> If you experience or witness
        behavior that violates these guidelines, report it through the app or
        contact us at
        <a href="mailto:info@boomger.com">info@boomger.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Consequences:</strong> Violations may result in content removal,
        warnings, temporary suspension, or permanent termination, depending on
        severity and repetition.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>8. Safety Tips</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Meet Safely:</strong> When meeting someone in person, choose a
        public place and inform a trusted friend or family member.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Trust Your Instincts:</strong> If a situation feels
        uncomfortable or unsafe, disengage and report the user.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Secure Your Account:</strong> Use a strong password and keep
        your login details private to protect your account.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>9. Community Engagement</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Positive Participation:</strong> Engage constructively in
        conversations and community groups. Encourage respectful dialogue and
        shared understanding.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Respect Diversity:</strong> Boomger celebrates diversity. Be
        open-minded and respectful of different backgrounds, cultures, and
        perspectives.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>10. Updates and Changes</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Stay Informed:</strong> We may update these Community Guidelines
        to reflect changes in our platform or policies. Continued use of Boomger
        constitutes acceptance of any updates.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <p>
        Boomger is built on trust, respect, and real connections. By following
        these guidelines, you help create a safer and more meaningful experience
        for everyone.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
